<chapter>
  <title>Introduction</title>
  <sect1>
    <title>Purpose of this Document</title>
    <para>
      This document is intended to be a living document that will
      house all the design work for OpenHPI 2.0.  Please feel free to
      edit any portion of this document at any time to bring it more
      in line with current thinking of the design.
    </para>
  </sect1>
  <sect1>
    <title>Topics to be Covered</title>
    <para>
      The following topics need to be covered as part of the OpenHPI
      2.0 design effort: Threading Model, OpenHPI Daemon, Plugins,
      Testing, HPI B changes, Scenarios, Utilities.
    </para>
  </sect1>
</chapter>
